## Inheritance Hierarchy Summary

```
ScriptableObject
└── BaseUnitData (abstract) — Identity, Health, Progression, Visuals
    ├── DefenderUnitData (abstract) — Economy (placementCost, sellRefundRate, upgradeCost)
    │   ├── CombatDefenderData — Offensive Stats, detectionRadius
    │   │   └── CreateAssetMenu: HKSV/Data/Units/Combat Defender
    │   └── ResourceDefenderData — produceCooldown, resourceAmount, resourcePrefab
    │       └── CreateAssetMenu: HKSV/Data/Units/Resource Defender
    └── EnemyUnitData — moveSpeed, detectionRadius, killReward, baseDamageOnReach
        └── CreateAssetMenu: HKSV/Data/Units/Enemy Unit
```

## OnValidate Chain

```
BaseUnitData.OnValidate()          → unlockCondition validation
  ↓
DefenderUnitData.OnValidate()      → base + faction auto-correct to Ally
  ↓
CombatDefenderData.OnValidate()    → base + attackRange vs detectionRadius
ResourceDefenderData.OnValidate()  → base + resourcePrefab null check

BaseUnitData.OnValidate()          → unlockCondition validation
  ↓
EnemyUnitData.OnValidate()         → base + faction auto-correct to Enemy
```

